## 14. Risk Management

Potential risk: Aptos ecosystem data sources may not be standardized.  
Mitigation: We will begin with public and documented data sources, then extend through opt-in integrations.

Potential risk: Early alert logic may produce false positives.  
Mitigation: We will use transparent reason codes, evidence fields, validation scenarios, and documentation.

Potential risk: Scope expansion.  
Mitigation: The first version will focus on the Aptos adapter, risk taxonomy, alert schema, sample alerts, documentation, and a reference consumer.

Potential risk: Localization quality.  
Mitigation: We will start with concise Chinese-language summaries and seek feedback from Chinese-speaking Aptos community members where possible.

